( ) Tj
T*
(## 5. Evaluation Snapshot) Tj
T*
(On benchmark v0 \(30 cases\), the prototype currently achieves:) Tj
T*
(- Violation recall: 1.0) Tj
T*
(- Root-cause exact match: 1.0) Tj
T*
(- Corrective compliance rate: 1.0) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(These results validate pipeline correctness on controlled traces; larger stress tests and human) Tj
T*
( audit studies remain future work.) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(## 6. Limitations and Ethics) Tj
T*
(The current benchmark is synthetic and policy scope is restricted to three families. Real deplo) Tj
T*
(yments require richer semantics \(cross-trace state, identity binding, partial observability\) an) Tj
T*
(d human oversight to avoid over-trusting automatic explanations.) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
